<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你看，<delay20 /><tag a="110" b="4" />！<delay frames="40" />
我這身服裝！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呵呵呵，<delay20 />沒錯<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
我就是被施展了名為「復活節」魔法的，<delay20 />
高興得不得了的<tag a="110" b="15" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />也看到了嗎？<delay frames="40" />
<colour id="3" />蹦蹦<colour id="65535" />那輕快的舞步<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可不是等閒之輩跳得出來的，<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />他配合著拍子跳啊跳的，<delay20 />
輕巧的步伐讓人感受不到絲毫重力<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
簡直就像是沒有穿衣服似的<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，你知道嗎？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />復活節的蛋<delay20 />
其實是可以吃的喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過，竟然要吃掉<delay20 />
猶如藝術品般美麗的蛋<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
真的有點不忍心啊～</message>
	<message label="011" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay20 />
你要記得抬頭看看天空喔。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />因為時不時會有彩色的氣球飛過呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要是有東西<delay20 />
可以把氣球射下來就好了<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />比方說，你熱情的視線！<delay frames="40" /><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />開玩笑的啦，哈哈！</message>
	<message label="012" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我在海邊散步的時候，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />找到一個色彩繽紛的瓶中信，<delay20 />
還以為是復活節的蛋呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然不知道把它放到海中的人在想什麼，<delay20 />
不過湊巧的是，它在復活節這一天<delay20 />
漂流到了<tag a="110" b="8" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呵呵呵，<delay20 />你也覺得吧？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這正是<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />復活節的奇蹟啊！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="104" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />也看到了嗎？<10_4 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不可思議的蛋<delay20 />
正在<tag a="110" b="8" />的天空中飄著<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我已經不覺得有什麼好驚訝的了。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />難道我也被施了魔法嗎？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是那名為「復活節」的魔法<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="105" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那個，<tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我剛才搖了一下眼前的樹，<delay20 />
突然有一顆彩色的蛋掉了下來。<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我嚇了一跳，但同時也相信……<delay frames="40" />
這就是復活節<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />送我的禮物，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="106" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我剛剛釣魚釣得正開心的時候，<delay20 />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />突然釣到了一個特別的東西，<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />本以為這是花紋美麗的魚<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Aha" target="actor" targetSpec="" />誰知道竟然是蛋！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這就是Easter Magic吧。</message>
	<message label="110" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="110_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay20 />
今天是復活節喔！<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />讓我們一起去收集很多<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />五顏六色的復活蛋吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="110_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天是復活節喔！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Dance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一起盡情地享受吧，<tag a="110" b="6" />！</message>
	<message label="111" attrib="00 00 02 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其實我<delay frames="40" />有點收集太多<delay frames="40" />
<colour id="1" /><anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" /><colour id="65535" />了<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果可以的話，<delay20 />我能用多的東西
來跟你交換其他種類的蛋嗎？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我們就互相各用<colour id="1" />3顆<colour id="65535" />來做交換吧。</message>
	<message label="111_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">好啊！</message>
	<message label="111_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">抱歉喔</message>
	<message label="112" attrib="00 00 02 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，我問你，<delay frames="40" />
你要不要用你身上的蛋，<delay20 />來和我的
<colour id="1" /><tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" /><colour id="65535" />做交換呢？
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我會給你<colour id="1" />3顆<colour id="65535" />這種蛋，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />然後你再給我<colour id="1" />3顆<colour id="65535" />其他種類的蛋。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我想這對我們雙方都有好處<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="112_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">好啊！</message>
	<message label="112_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">抱歉喔</message>
	<message label="113" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />咦，真的嗎？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那麼你可以告訴我，<delay20 />
你要用哪種蛋和我交換嗎？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="114" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這樣才對嘛！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那麼我們<delay20 />趕快來交換吧，<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你要用哪種蛋來交換呢？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="116" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Thank you，<tag a="110" b="4" />！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你願意和我交換真是幫大忙了，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />之後有機會再麻煩你囉，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="117" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哦～<delay20 />
你給我的蛋也很不錯呢～！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay20 />謝謝你！</message>
	<message label="118" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這樣啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
抱歉提出這麼唐突的請求，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我會再去問問看其他人的，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="119" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不，<delay20 />沒關係啦<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
是我不好，<delay20 />我太受
<colour id="1" /><anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" /><colour id="65535" />歡迎了。</message>
	<message label="120" attrib="00 00 02 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />用<colour id="1" />3顆<colour id="65535" />你的<colour id="1" /><tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x1" /><colour id="65535" />，<delay20 />
和<colour id="1" />3顆<colour id="65535" />我的<colour id="1" /><tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" /><colour id="65535" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />做交換沒錯吧？</message>
	<message label="120_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">OK！</message>
	<message label="120_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">還是算了</message>
	<message label="121" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好，<delay20 />那麼交易就成立了！</message>
	<message label="122" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好，那麼<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 /><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />咦？<delay frames="40" />
你的持有物品不是滿了嗎？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />等你整理後再過來吧。</message>
</msbt>